text: Kern County is a county in the U.S. state of California. As of the 2020 census, the population was 909,235. The county seat is Bakersfield. == Notable people == * Donald Glover - Actor, rapper, and singer * Mark Hoppus - Musician and producer * Donald Cheney - Crew (film/tv) * Rob Bonta - Politician == References == Category:1866 establishments in California
